===現役機隊===
截至2021年6月，聯合航空共有837架飛機，平均機齡為16.3年,擁有以下飛機<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.unitedcontinentalholdings.com/documents/FactSheet.pdf?file=united_factsheet.pdf&type=pdf |title=United Airlines Fact Sheet |publisher=www.unitedcontinentalholdings.com |date= |accessdate=2013-02-17 |archive-date=2013-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116045411/http://www.unitedcontinentalholdings.com/documents/FactSheet.pdf?file=united_factsheet.pdf&type=pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://aerotransport.org/php/go.php?query=operator&qstring=United+Airlines&where=91636&luck= |title=United Airlines (ATDB) |publisher=Aerotransport.org |date= |accessdate=2012-12-25 |archive-date=2013-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105210542/http://aerotransport.org/php/go.php?query=operator&qstring=United+Airlines&where=91636&luck= |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.planespotters.net/airline/United-Airlines |title=United Airlines Fleet |publisher=www.planespotters.net |date= |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130416225215/http://www.planespotters.net/Airline/United-Airlines |dead-url=no }}</ref>：
