== 争议事件 ==
*戴夫·卡罗尔在2008年乘坐联合航空期间，发现地勤人员粗暴抛卸托运货物，并发现自己的泰勒吉他严重损坏，在和航空公司商讨赔偿无果后，创作了歌曲《[[联合航空砸烂了我的吉他|联合航空砸烂了我的吉他]]》并制作讽刺影片上传到[[YouTube|YouTube]]，引发舆论关注并对航空公司进行抵制，引发公关危机，最终间接影响其股价，航空公司公关总监致电向戴夫道歉并作出赔偿。
*2012年，一名[[創傷後壓力症候群|創傷後壓力症候群]]（PTSD）的美國退伍軍人施塔內克（Jim Stanek）從伊拉克欲搭乘聯合航空回美國時，因航班延誤被迫滯留三天，期間其輔助犬兩度遭聯航職員用腳踢，甚至當施塔內克向聯航職員協助確認電子郵件內容時，遭到職員反問施塔內克是否腦殘，令施塔內克非常難受。聯合航空發言人事後出面表示，正與施塔內克連絡了解詳情。 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rescuedheroesfoundation.org/jim-stanek-and-sarge-their-story/ |title=Jim Stanek and Sarge – Their Story |publisher=Rescued Heroes Foundation |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170413070739/http://www.rescuedheroesfoundation.org/jim-stanek-and-sarge-their-story/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.kpbs.org/news/2012/oct/10/tension-growing-ptsd-service-dogs-veterans/ |title=Tension Growing Over Role Of PTSD Service Dogs For Veterans |agency=Associated Press |date=October 10, 2012 |location=San Diego |publisher=KPBS |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412143706/http://www.kpbs.org/news/2012/oct/10/tension-growing-ptsd-service-dogs-veterans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/crime/interview-jim-stanek-talks-service-dogs-for-vets-project-delta-of-mn/vp-BBvtDHr |title=Interview: Jim Stanek Talks Service Dogs For Vets, Project Delta Of MN |publisher=MSN |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412143755/http://www.msn.com/en-us/news/crime/interview-jim-stanek-talks-service-dogs-for-vets-project-delta-of-mn/vp-BBvtDHr |archivedate=2017年4月12日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aetv.com/shows/dogs-of-war/cast/jim-stanek |title=Dogs of War – Cast – Jim Stanek |work=A&E |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412143231/http://www.aetv.com/shows/dogs-of-war/cast/jim-stanek |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/22/jim-stanek-united-airlines-service-dog-sarge_n_1692951.html |title=Jim Stanek, Disabled Veteran Says United Airlines Staff Kicked His Service Dog, Asked If He Was ‘Retarded’ |author=Laura Hibbard |date=July 22, 2012 |work=Huffington Post |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170414030859/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/22/jim-stanek-united-airlines-service-dog-sarge_n_1692951.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kpbs.org/news/2012/jul/24/veteran-united-airlines-mistreated-ptsd-dog/ |title=Veteran Says United Airlines Mistreated PTSD Service Dog |author=Beth Ford Roth |date=July 24, 2012 |location=San Diego |work=KPBS News |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418002620/http://www.kpbs.org/news/2012/jul/24/veteran-united-airlines-mistreated-ptsd-dog/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2015年，一名塔希拉．阿瑪德（Tahera Ahmad）女性穆斯林乘客，在機上向空服員要一瓶未開瓶的可樂，但空服員不但以公司規定拒絕，還指稱未開瓶的[[易開罐|易開罐]]有可能被當成恐怖攻擊的武器，讓阿瑪德認為遭到宗教歧視。聯合航空後來對阿瑪德致歉。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/30/us/united-flight-muslim-chaplain/ |title=United apologizes after in-flight discrimination claim |author=Ray Sanchez |date=June 23, 2015 |work=CNN |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170416185808/http://www.cnn.com/2015/05/30/us/united-flight-muslim-chaplain/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/02/tahera-ahmad-united-airlines-soda-can-discrimination |title=Tahera Ahmad: 'This isn't about me and a soda can, it's about systemic injustice' |date=June 2, 2015 |work=The Guardian |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412144530/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2015/jun/02/tahera-ahmad-united-airlines-soda-can-discrimination |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2015年5月，一位聯合航空機長在收到機上有一名[[自閉症|自閉症]]乘客時，將其一家人趕下飛機，並表示「載患有自閉症的妳女兒讓自己很不舒服」。事情爆發後迅速引起網友注目，ABC新聞頻道在Yahoo.com上發佈的相關報道不到24小時就收到一萬多條評論，不少人嚴厲批評聯合航空對有特殊需求的乘客過於冷漠。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/autistic-girl-removed-from-flight-after-emergency-landing/ |title=Autistic girl removed from flight after emergency landing |author=Carter Evans |date=May 10, 2015 |work=CBS News |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420042051/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/autistic-girl-removed-from-flight-after-emergency-landing/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://wgntv.com/2015/05/11/family-fights-back-after-teenage-daughter-with-autism-kicked-off-flight/ |title=Family fights back after teenage daughter with autism kicked off flight |author=WBN Web Desk |date= |location=Chicago |publisher=WGN TV |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412224553/http://wgntv.com/2015/05/11/family-fights-back-after-teenage-daughter-with-autism-kicked-off-flight/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/14/travel/a-range-of-reactions-to-airlines-removal-of-autistic-child.html |title=A Range of Reactions to Airline’s Removal of Autistic Child |author=Rachel Lee Haris |date=May 14, 2015 |work=New York Times |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170808115030/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/14/travel/a-range-of-reactions-to-airlines-removal-of-autistic-child.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/woman-claims-daughter-autism-kicked-off-united-airlines/story?id=30926832 |title=Woman Claims She and Daughter With Autism Were Kicked Off United Airlines Flight |author=Emily Shapaire |date=May 11, 2015 |work=ABC News |accessdate=April 12, 2017 |archive-date=2017-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417083715/http://abcnews.go.com/US/woman-claims-daughter-autism-kicked-off-united-airlines/story?id=30926832 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2017年3月26日，2名女性乘客因下半身只穿著緊身褲，遭聯合航空員工要求這兩位少女必須在緊身褲上面加穿洋裝或是換褲才可搭機，否則就禁止登機。事件爆發後迅速引起爭議，不少網民批評聯合航空此舉是性別歧視。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170327/s00005/1490589861339 |title= 緊身褲女孩被拒登機惹爭議　聯合航空：通行證乘客不可穿瑜伽或緊身褲 |publisher= 明報 |date= 2017-03-27 |author=  |accessdate= 2017-04-17 |archive-date= 2017-04-18 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20170418081539/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170327/s00005/1490589861339 |dead-url= no }}</ref>然而，聯合航空發言人蓋林（Jonathan Guerin）出面澄清該2名女性乘客是通行乘客（pass travelers），即聯合航空員工或其眷屬，提及公司其中之一要求就是員工不可只穿瑜伽褲或緊身褲上飛機，並強調一般乘客不會因只穿緊身褲或瑜伽褲而被拒登機。<ref>{{cite news |url= https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/2366869 |title= 少女穿緊身褲被禁止登機？聯合航空澄清 |publisher= 聯合新聞網 |date= 2017-03-27 |author= 顏伶如 |accessdate= 2017-04-17 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20170418082216/https://money.udn.com/money/story/5641/2366869 |archivedate= 2017-04-18 |deadurl= yes }}</ref><ref name=united-leggings>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/26/us/united-airlines-leggings.html|title=After Barring Girls for Leggings, United Airlines Defends Decision|publisher=New York Times|date=March 26, 2017|accessdate=April 10, 2017|archive-date=2017-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418165238/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/03/26/us/united-airlines-leggings.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*身長1.3米的已故「世界第一巨兔」Darius，是世界紀錄保持者。牠生有現時約10個月大、身形已達90厘米的兒子Simon。可是，Simon的飼主、英國前模特兒愛德華茲（Annette Edwards）原本花費逾2千英鎊，把Simon託運送往美國給一位名人新飼主，但在2017年4月19日，聯航的飛機從[[倫敦|倫敦]][[希斯洛機場|希斯洛機場]]飛抵[[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[奧黑爾國際機場|奧黑爾國際機場]]後，卻發現Simon竟在貨艙死亡。而Simon在登機前，獸醫還診斷牠健康狀況良好。聯航執行長孟諾茲（Oscar Munoz）表示道歉。飼主則指責聯航不肯給她翻查[[閉路電視|閉路電視]]片段，更擅自把兔屍火化，企圖隱瞞真相。愛德華茲相信，Simon的死是因為聯航職員把Simon放進冰箱裏，但聯航發言人矢口否認。<ref>[https://udn.com/news/story/6813/2426916 《又是聯航！英國巨兔在機上離奇死亡》] {{Wayback|url=https://udn.com/news/story/6813/2426916 |date=20170427072240 }}，《聯合新聞網》2017年4月26日。[http://www.worldjournal.com/4946405/ 《巨兔搭機死亡 孟諾茲又道歉》] {{Wayback|url=http://www.worldjournal.com/4946405/ |date=20171201034424 }}，《世界日報》2017年4月28日。[http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/201704300111-1.aspx 《聯合航空疑又出包 誤把名種巨兔凍死》] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/201704300111-1.aspx |date=20170503095345 }}，《中央通訊社》2017年4月30日。[http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170501/bknint-20170501152041496-0501_17011_001.html 《巨兔上機後離奇死亡　聯合航空涉擅自火化》] {{Wayback|url=http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170501/bknint-20170501152041496-0501_17011_001.html |date=20170504140233 }}，香港《東方日報》2017年5月1日。</ref>最後愛德華茲獲聯合航空賠償，以換取她不再向外界講述事件，包括賠償金額都沒有公開。<ref>[http://www.exmoo.com/article/32128.html 《巨兔航機中凍死　主人獲聯合航空賠數萬美元》] {{Wayback|url=http://www.exmoo.com/article/32128.html |date=20180819051251 }}，澳門《力報》2017年5月8日。[http://toronto.singtao.ca/1730600/2017-05-08/post-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E8%88%AA%E5%B7%A8%E5%85%94%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8C-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%9F%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0/?variant=zh-hk 《美聯航“巨兔死亡案”：賠償主人後　買家也索賠》] {{Wayback|url=http://toronto.singtao.ca/1730600/2017-05-08/post-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E8%88%AA%E5%B7%A8%E5%85%94%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%A1%88%EF%BC%9A%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E4%B8%BB%E4%BA%BA%E5%BE%8C-%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%9F%E7%B4%A2%E8%B3%A0/?variant=zh-hk |date=20171201035004 }}，香港《星島日報》2017年5月8日。[http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170503/bknint-20170503151220010-0503_17011_001.html 《巨兔乘聯合航空疑凍死　飼主獲賠數萬美元》] {{Wayback|url=http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170503/bknint-20170503151220010-0503_17011_001.html |date=20170506010652 }}，香港《東方日報》2017年5月3日。</ref>
*2017年2月16日，以電動輪椅代步的加拿大68歲傷健人士Stearn Hodge，被聯航及加拿大航空運輸安全局(CATSA)職員禁止攜帶輪椅的鋰電池及後備電池上機，違反國際航空運輸協會(IATA)守則，職員也拒抗查看IATA批文及聆聽苦主的解釋，還建議獨臂的苦主改用手推輪椅，結果令苦主在其後旅程的大部份時間無法使用輪椅，甚至要爬行上洗手間，感到屈辱。聯航事後向苦主道歉，賠償苦主及其妻子一張800美元旅遊禮券。事件的追討爭持多年，苦主委託律師於2019年5月9日入稟請求聯邦法官強制人權委員會審理此案。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.am730.com.hk/news/新聞/【最屈辱】輪椅電池被聯航禁帶上機-殘障男要爬住度假有片-171205 |title=【最屈辱】輪椅電池被聯航禁帶上機 殘障男要爬住度假(有片) |date=2019-05-04 |work=am730 |accessdate=2022-01-03 |archive-date=2020-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031190350/https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%9C%80%E5%B1%88%E8%BE%B1%E3%80%91%E8%BC%AA%E6%A4%85%E9%9B%BB%E6%B1%A0%E8%A2%AB%E8%81%AF%E8%88%AA%E7%A6%81%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%8A%E6%A9%9F-%E6%AE%98%E9%9A%9C%E7%94%B7%E8%A6%81%E7%88%AC%E4%BD%8F%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-171205 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/amputee-claims-discrimination-after-airport-security-takes-batteries-1.5109369 |title='I had to crawl': Amputee seeks damages after United Airlines and airport security seize scooter batteries |date=2019-04-28 |work=加拿大廣播公司 |accessdate=2019-05-02 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502213315/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/amputee-claims-discrimination-after-airport-security-takes-batteries-1.5109369 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
*2017年6月6日，中国女子网球手[[张帅_(网球运动员)|张帅]]乘搭聯合航空航班準備由[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]飛往[[華盛頓|華盛頓]]時，一名聯合航空地勤在登機閘口前未經她允許，強行拿走她的網球包並說她的球包超出大小標準。經訴說後地勤仍是不讓該網球包登機，並要求張帥託運該球包或乘搭其他航班，職員更企圖搶走拍袋和她的護照，拉扯期間張的登機證被撕爛。張帥表示自己這麼多年每週旅行，球員大部份都能帶拍包上飛機的，她並領教到聯航態度惡劣囂張的一面<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2017/06/08/a1328242.html |title=中國網球手張帥斥美聯航職員搶袋 撕爛登機證 |date=2017-06-08 |work=新唐人電視台 |accessdate=2017-06-24 |archive-date=2017-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915064653/http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2017/06/08/a1328242.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170608/bkn-20170608134052042-0608_00822_001.html|title=網球手張帥斥聯合航空職員搶袋　撕爛登機證|date=2017-06-08|work=東網|language=zh-yue|accessdate=2017-06-24|archive-date=2017-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612005220/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170608/bkn-20170608134052042-0608_00822_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。數天後，聯航通過[[Twitter|Twitter]]回應事件及向張帥致歉，稱：「我們對你在旅途中遭遇的問題困惑，感到非常的抱歉，可以私信告知我們你的聯繫方式，以便進行溝通解決事件嗎？」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170610/00176_012.html |title=聯合航空向網球手張帥致歉 |date=2017-06-10 |work=東方日報 (香港) |accessdate=2017-06-24 |archive-date=2017-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612000807/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170610/00176_012.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*2017年6月29日，兩歲大男童機位被搶，被逼坐媽媽膝蓋<ref>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2o6zNhxNdL8 {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2o6zNhxNdL8 |date=20200325202309 }} |title= 聯合航空 - 兩歲大男童機位被搶，被逼坐媽媽膝蓋 UA takes seat away from 2yrs old kid</ref>。

===2017年联航快运暴力驱赶乘客事件===
{{main|联航快运3411号班机事件}}
2017年4月9日晚上<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39554421 |title=United Airlines: Passenger forcibly removed from flight |accessdate=2017-04-11 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411192714/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-39554421 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，一名亚裔乘客被强行拖下共和航空运营的[[联航快运|联航快运]]的班机。当时登机已经完成，联合航空却称飞机需要为机组人员寻求4个座位，因此要求4名乘客离开满员的航班<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/3275/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-3275/business-insider%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%82%BA%E5%9B%9B%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%90%AD%E6%A9%9F%E8%B6%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%90%BD%E6%A9%9F |title=聯合航空為四職員搭機趕人落機 |access-date=2017-04-12 |archive-date=2021-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712004530/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/3275/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA-3275/business-insider%EF%BC%9A%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%82%BA%E5%9B%9B%E8%81%B7%E5%93%A1%E6%90%AD%E6%A9%9F%E8%B6%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%90%BD%E6%A9%9F |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 聯合航空公司一开始提供每人16張50美元分次使用的聯航折價卷作為補償（總額800美元），但是没有乘客自愿离开，于是联合航空使用抽籤決定选择4名需要下機的乘客。其中有一位69岁的亚裔乘客拒绝下機要求，遭到航警暴力對待，並被強行帶離飛機<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/10/business/united-flight-passenger-dragged.html?_r=0 |title=United Airlines Passenger Is Dragged From an Overbooked Flight |accessdate=2017-04-11 |archive-date=2017-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417204156/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/10/business/united-flight-passenger-dragged.html?_r=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/business/ct-united-passenger-dragged-fallout-stock-0412-biz-20170411-story.html |title=United faces more questions as dragged passenger hires high-powered attorney |accessdate=2017-04-11 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411221356/http://www.chicagotribune.com/business/ct-united-passenger-dragged-fallout-stock-0412-biz-20170411-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2017-04-11/united-is-feeling-the-sway-of-consumers-in-asia |title=United Is Feeling the Sway of Consumers in Asia |accessdate=2017-04-11 |archive-date=2017-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170411205215/https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2017-04-11/united-is-feeling-the-sway-of-consumers-in-asia |dead-url=no }}</ref>。涉及争议的乘客为美籍[[越南华裔|越南华裔]]醫生杜成德<ref>[http://www.courier-journal.com/story/news/local/2017/04/11/david-dao-passenger-removed-united-flight-doctor-troubled-past/100318320/ David Dao, passenger removed from United flight, now in spotlight]</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://foreignpolicy.com/2017/04/11/chinese-blame-america-for-united-airlines/|title=Chinese Blame America for United Airlines|work=FP|access-date=2017-04-12|archive-date=2017-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412103913/http://foreignpolicy.com/2017/04/11/chinese-blame-america-for-united-airlines/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=kimberlyyam>{{cite news|title=After United Controversy, Chinese Social Media Users Express Outrage|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/united-social-media-controversy_us_58ecde88e4b0df7e20455dbf|agency=The Huffington Post|publisher=Kimberly Yam|date=April 11, 2017|accessdate=2017-04-13|archive-date=2017-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170413111827/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/entry/united-social-media-controversy_us_58ecde88e4b0df7e20455dbf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

